at all vehicles you have registered be currently covered with the required =
limits of liability insurance or other security as provided under <a href=
=3D"https://legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=3D88604" target=3D"new">R.S. 32:8=
61</a> et al. &nbsp;The law is enforced by civil and criminal penalty.</li>
            <li class=3D"list-group-item">Changes in personal information, =
including address, are not allowed by using the Internet or mail-in method =
of renewal. &nbsp;If you require any changes, you must visit your <a href=
=3D"https://expresslane.org/" target=3D"new">local Office of Motor Vehicles=
</a> for issuance of a new driver's license.</li>
